CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper July 28, 1945, pg. 14, reads: "Birthday Party - Rozendo Beasley, son of Mrs. Nancy Beasley, of 7333 Frankstown Avenue, was feted recently at a party celebrating his eleventh birthday. The party was given by his sister, Miss Jean Beasley. A crowd of youthful merry-makers attended, to make the date memorable. - Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: Woman and children gathered for 11th birthday party of Rozendo Beasley, possibly including his mother Nancy Beasley and sister Jean Beasley, gathered in Beasley home, 7333 Frankstown Avenue
